# AI Agents SaaS Platform Roadmap

This roadmap outlines the evolution of the platform from the initial MVP to a fully scalable AI agent ecosystem.

---

# Version 1.0 — Initial SaaS Platform

Status: Completed

Core functionality implemented:

* Multi-tenant architecture
* Agent execution engine
* Tool integration system
* Agent memory storage
* Async execution with Celery
* Execution monitoring
* Billing system
* Docker deployment
* Cloud deployment configs

---

# Version 1.1 — Agent Improvements

Planned features:

* Streaming responses
* Agent execution timeline
* Improved error handling
* Agent execution retry system
* Better prompt debugging

